About

On month 8 of our software engineering programme at Alx African we where required to pair up and develop a portfolio project. We paired up as a group of 2 (Mbali Ramakgasha & Muhammed Muburak). We both located in different countries and as we share information about our personality, experience, practices and so one we realised the is so much to discover beyond what's trending on available social media and we decided to create an app to showcase the culture and art of the people. we needed it to be very interactive and controlled information about culture and arts. The project took us 5 to 7 weeks to complete, which was quite amazing considering the challenges we had like power cuts, distance and the war.

Explore &

Learn

We dive into a rich tapestry of cultural practices from around the globe. Discover traditional dances, vibrant music, tantalizing cuisines, ancient rituals, festive celebrations, and exquisite crafts, all waiting to be explored. Immerse yourself in a world of creativity as you discover various art forms, from classical masterpieces to contemporary expressions. With our platform, the journey of cultural discovery and artistic exploration knows no bounds.

Showcase &

Interact

Users and Artists have the spotlight to exhibit their diverse array of artworks, spanning from paintings and sculptures to digital creations and beyond. But it's not just about displaying; users are invited to actively engage by sharing their own posts, expressing thoughts, and reacting to others' contributions. This dynamic interaction fosters a vibrant community where creativity thrives, connections are made, and inspiration knows no boundaries.

Find your next adventure

Indulge your passion for art and culture with our Events feature, a dynamic platform tailored to your interests. From vibrant festivals to intimate workshops, discover a diverse array of curated experiences designed to ignite your creativity and expand your horizons. Engage with artists, explore new mediums, and immerse yourself in thought-provoking discussions that celebrate the richness of human expression. With our comprehensive calendar and personalized recommendations, finding your next cultural adventure has never been easier. Join our community of enthusiasts and embark on a journey of discovery with us today.
